% Features: Single Temperature Adjustment:
% Adjusts the current temperature incrementally by up to 25% of the difference from the target temperature.
% Logs the adjustment magnitude for transparency.
% Dynamic Temperature Control:
% Simulates temperature control over multiple cycles.
% Stops early if the target temperature is reached within a 0.1°C threshold.
% Outputs the temperature at each cycle and the final temperature after simulation.
